title: [Blighted Forest, Treetop]
description: A break in the branches to the west prohibits crossing in that direction.  However, the wide limbs offer easy access to neighboring trees on the north and east.  Smaller branches create a tunnel effect, with the brightly colored plumage of birds dotting the dark foliage.
